{"title_page": "2016 Campbell Fighting Camels football team", "text_new": "{{short description|American college football season}}\n{{NCAATeamSeason\n| mode = football\n| year = 2016\n| team=Campbell Fighting Camels\n| image=Campbell Athletics wordmark.png\n| image_size= 250\n| conference= Pioneer Football League\n| division= \n| short_conf= PFL\n| STATSRank = \n| FCSCoachRank = \n| record = 5\u20135\n| conf_record = 3\u20134\n| head_coach= [[Mike Minter]]\n| hc_year = 4th\n| off_coach= Landon Mariani\n| oc_year = 4th as OC 10th overall \n| def_coach= Craig Cox\n| dc_year = 4th \n| off_scheme= \n| def_scheme=\n| stadium= [[Barker\u2013Lane Stadium]]<br>(Capacity: 5,000)\n| champion = \n| bowl = \n| bowl_result =  \n}}\n{{2016 Pioneer Football League standings}}\nThe '''2016 Campbell Fighting Camels football team''' represented [[Campbell University]] in the [[2016 NCAA Division I FCS football season]]. They were led by fourth-year head coach [[Mike Minter]] and played their home games at [[Barker\u2013Lane Stadium]]. They were members of the [[Pioneer Football League]]. They finished the season 5\u20135, 3\u20134 in PFL play to finish in sixth place.\n\n==Schedule==\n{{CFB schedule\n| rankyear = 2016\n\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = September 3\n| time = 4:00 PM\n| w/l = w\n| nonconf = y\n| opponent = {{cfb link|year=2016|team=Bluefield College Rams|title=Bluefield}}\n| site_stadium = [[Barker\u2013Lane Stadium]]\n| site_cityst = [[Buies Creek, North Carolina|Buies Creek, NC]]\n| tv = {{URL|1=http://bigsouthsports.com/watch/?Archive=17|2=BSN}}\n| score = 59\u20137\n| attend = 5,230\n}}\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = September 10\n| time = 6:00 PM\n| w/l = w\n| nonconf = y\n| away = y\n| opponent = {{cfb link|year=2016|team=Chowan Hawks|title=Chowan}}\n| site_stadium = [[Garrison Stadium]]\n| site_cityst = [[Murfreesboro, North Carolina|Murfreesboro, NC]]\n| tv = \n| score = 47\u201314\n| attend = 3,480\n}}\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = September 17\n| time = 6